text: Amine Oudrhiri (born 4 November 1992) is a French professional footballer of Moroccan descent who plays as a midfielder for Primeira Liga side Farense. ==Club career== After spending time in the semi-professional leagues, Oudrhiri joined Nantes in 2013. He was loaned out for half a season to Arles-Avignon in February 2015 where he made his full professional debut the same month, in a 1–0 Ligue 2 defeat against Nîmes.
